sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant GUI as Streamlit GUI
  participant API as FastAPI API
  participant Search as OpenSearch
  participant LLM as vLLM/RAG
  participant Graph as Graph Services
  User->>GUI: login, choose tenant, enter query
  GUI->>API: POST /search/
  API->>Search: hybrid search
  Search-->>API: ranked hits
  API-->>GUI: items
  User->>GUI: select rows
  GUI->>API: POST /chat/ or /papers/summarize_conditioned
  API->>LLM: prompt with pinned context
  LLM-->>API: answer/citations
  API-->>GUI: SSE or JSON response
  GUI->>API: POST /triplets/graph/build
  API->>Graph: semantic triplet filtering
  API-->>GUI: triple_ids
  GUI->>API: GET /triplets/graph/view
